{
  "texts": [
    "Agents in TextCraft aim to craft target items using available resources and a set of defined actions.",
    "The test split contains 200 samples.",
    "Following Prasad et al. (2023), we employed GPT-3.5-turbo for WebShop and gpt-3.5-turbo-instruct for TextCraft.",
    "Due to the lack of tool document and the monotonous nature of the tasks, we did not engage in agent generation.",
    "Instead, we utilized the predefined agents from ADAPT."
  ]
}